uide business outcomes Managing outside counsel, including budgeting Providing creative, innovative, and effective legal solutions for business stakeholders on routinely short timelines. Collaborating closely with colleagues in the legal team What We Look For In You (ie. Job Requirements) Approximately four - seven years of relevant legal experience, including at a law firm or regulatory agency Exceptional legal writing skills Exceptional organizational skills Experience advising on regulatory engagement Excellent judgement, analytic rigor, and business pragmatism Must be active and in good standing in one State Bar in the United States A whip-smart and detail-oriented attorney with solid management and leadership skills Nice to haves Interest in policy matters relating to the cryptocurrency industry Benefits at Coinbase Health, Dental, and Vision insurance covered at 100% for employees and 80% for dependents HSA plan with company seed Disability and Life Insurance 401(k) plan with company match $260 monthly Commuter Benefit Monthly Gym Benefit Volunteer Time Off Fertility Counseling and Benefits Learning and Development stipend 18 weeks paid Parental Leave Meals and Snacks provided onsite The option of getting paid in digital currency 7 year post termination option exercise window (for employees who stay 2 years or more) vs. the industry standard 90 days ", 
